<subSubSection id="4946662DA46E8A88CB25202229685C05" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="6960B602F74DD546270FAD0524523090" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="057527055D28C146932303DAD3008D45" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">
Only known from China (Fujian, Guizhou, Hubei, Hunan, Chongqing) (
<bibRefCitation id="49DFDEF95E335EABBCC8C60E9E49DE77" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3887.3.4" author="Jia, F-L" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" pagination="354 - 376" refId="B13" refString="Jia, F-L, Aston, P, Fikacek, M, 2014. Review of the Chinese species of the genus Coelostoma Brulle, 1835 (Coleoptera: Hydrophilidae: Sphaeridiinae). Zootaxa 3887 (3): 354 - 376, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3887.3.4" title="Review of the Chinese species of the genus Coelostoma Brulle, 1835 (Coleoptera: Hydrophilidae: Sphaeridiinae)." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3887.3.4" volume="3887" year="2014">Jia et al. 2014</bibRefCitation>
). New record for Fujian, Guizhou, and Chongqing.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
